ont-size: large;\">共产党</span></span></strong>又打到來啦<br />\n會共晒你的錢，仲敢唔敢收佢地的蛇齋餅粽？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uGWiDxi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuGWiDxi.gif&h=e2aa19f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好人一世平安"}]}